generated_description: forest home animal clinic doggie day camp & boarding is a dog day care center and boarding facility located in franklin, wi. they offer indoor and outdoor environments for dogs to play and exercise in a supervised playtime with other friendly dogs and caring counselors. the day camp is run differently from other dog daycare centers in the area, with a staff-to-dog ratio and a maximum of 10 dogs per camp counselor. dogs are never left unsupervised in a group and are provided with appropriate size enclosures or large lodges for those who do not do well in small spaces. the staff is committed to giving dogs a fun and safe experience, and they post photos of the dogs daily.
